09:26.000 --> 09:30.000
It's a very effective thing.

09:30.000 --> 09:31.000
In terms of evolution,

09:31.000 --> 09:32.000
of course,

09:32.000 --> 09:34.000
as an individual,

09:34.000 --> 09:39.000
