09:44.000 --> 09:46.000
We need to interact with these people for a long time.

09:46.000 --> 09:49.000
Don't interact with another group of people for a long time.

09:49.000 --> 09:51.000
This ability becomes very important,

09:51.000 --> 09:52.000
very functional,

09:52.000 --> 09:54.000
and very effective.

