13:53.000 --> 13:55.000
As a person,

13:55.000 --> 13:56.000
I see this characteristic

13:56.000 --> 13:58.000
in my partner.

13:58.000 --> 13:59.000
The first two words,

13:59.000 --> 14:00.000
Perceived Partner.

14:00.000 --> 14:02.000
